node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Russell Wilson on August 16, 2021 tagging @yougotmojo, and @rwnflflag. May be an image of 2 people, people standing, outdoors and text that says 'GOT YOU MOJO x NFL FLAG'.

node.text:
I’m really excited about this one! @yougotmojo is now LIVE with flag football in partnership with @nflflag. The app now features flag coaching content for practices (coaches, you can build them in one tap!) and activities to do at home, and includes the entire NFL FLAG playbook.

I really wish I’d had MOJO for football when I was growing up… can’t wait to use it with my kids! #YouGotMOJO #MOJOxNFLFLAG

Link in bio to download. 🙏🏾

node.text:
Win’s first steps! Witnessing Win walk on the practice field for the first time.. it hit me that God orders our steps. “In their hearts humans plan their course, but the Lord establishes their steps.”
‭‭Proverbs‬ ‭16:9‬ ‭NIV‬‬
So many times in life I would always want to control & decide what is best or what I should do. Going into year 10 & watching my kids grow has given me such a perspective in life of a “Rookie.”
Knowing that in the Game of Life that Jesus is the Quarterback. I thank You Jesus for allowing me to Let Go & Let God! I praise You!!! 🙏🏾🙌🏾
